videos.description: In the final seconds of the first half, West Virginia's Tarik Phillip steals the inbounds pass, then feeds it to Esa Ahmad for a ferocious dunk, putting the Mountaineers up 50-22 at the half over Eastern Kentucky.
videos.headline: WVU ends half with authority
